next big scoop is on our patch.

105
00:07:26,109 --> 00:07:26,809
I'm not having it.

106
00:07:26,810 --> 00:07:28,390
I want them shut down.

107
00:07:28,490 --> 00:07:30,470
Are fraud all right with this, guv?
I'll talk them through it

108
00:07:30,570 --> 00:07:34,270
