I want round-the-clock surveillance.

109
00:07:34,370 --> 00:07:36,410
Albert Stroller. The Roper.
Been grifting since the Boer War.

110
00:07:36,411 --> 00:07:39,609
He's got contacts all over the city.

111
00:07:39,610 --> 00:07:40,950
Ash "Three Socks" Morgan.
The Fixer.

112
00:07:41,049 --> 00:07:43,249
He knows more tricks
than a cartful of monkeys.

113
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:46,730
But this is where we start.
Sean and Emma Kennedy.

114
00:07:46,731 --> 00:07:47,729
The newbies.

115
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:50,390
Stroller found them making
short cons on the street

116
00:07:50,391 --> 00:07:51,489
and brought them into
the fold.

117
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:52,810
He and Stone are training them up,

118
00:07:52,881 --> 00:07:54,209
